      "title": "Sri Lanka president suspends parliament, new session on Aug 03",
      "author": "",
      "body_lines": [
        "ECONOMYNEXT \u2013 Sri Lanka President Ranil Wickremesinghe has suspended parliament and recalled it on August 03 in a new session, in an expected move.",
        "The parliament is prorogued with effect from midnight on July 28, he said by gazette notice.",
        "The action dissolves existing committees in parliament allowing new members to be appointed."
      ],
